title: Oakland Athletics average ticket price 2006 to 2019
yAxis: Average ticket price in U.S. dollars
summary: The chart at hand is a line chart where the x axis denotes Year and a y axis denotes Average ticket price in U.S. dollars. In total the number of data points it has is 13.
Overall Average ticket price in U.S. dollars has increased over the Year.
Average ticket price in U.S. dollars is slightly increasing from 2006 to 2008, slightly decreasing from 2008 to 2010, and finally roughly constant from 2010 to 2019.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2007 and 2008.
Maximum Average ticket price in U.S. dollars, about 29.2 was reported at Year 2008
Minimum Average ticket price in U.S. dollars about 21.52 was reached at Year 2011
